      <hedline>
        <hl1>Color Me Furious</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>There's nothing to make me want to chuck my compact fluorescent light bulbs and leave my car idling in the school pickup line more than a room of billionaires' wives patting themselves on their designer backs for buying $140 eco-friendly cleaning kits for the household staff.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>There's nothing to make me want to chuck my compact fluorescent light bulbs and leave my car idling in the school pickup line more than a room of billionaires' wives patting themselves on their designer backs for buying $140 eco-friendly cleaning kits for the household staff.</p>
        <p>I'm sure those women have a pile of inspiring stories in them, but that wasn't one of them.</p>
        <p>Teresa DiFalco  McMinnville, Ore.</p>
      </block>
